1
00:01:30,360 --> 00:01:37,440
=Have a Crush on You=

2
00:01:38,060 --> 00:01:40,980
=Episode 5=

3
00:01:46,179 --> 00:01:49,179
Cerebral parasitic disease
is quite rare.

4
00:02:01,579 --> 00:02:02,819
Why did you come here?

5
00:02:02,819 --> 00:02:04,219
Don't you know that
the other side is occupied?

6
00:02:04,219 --> 00:02:05,660
Go back and rest well.

7
00:02:09,500 --> 00:02:10,459
Dr. Ruan,

8
00:02:11,140 --> 00:02:12,300
you're pretty bold.

9
00:02:12,340 --> 00:02:13,700
You operated on the patient before

10
00:02:13,739 --> 00:02:15,220
the attending doctor arrived.

11
00:02:15,379 --> 00:02:17,019
It was an emergency.

12
00:02:17,019 --> 00:02:18,860
His intracranial pressure
kept rising non-stop.

13
00:02:19,019 --> 00:02:20,259
Why didn't you inject him with Mannitol?

14
00:02:20,659 --> 00:02:22,220
We've already done that.

15
00:02:22,340 --> 00:02:24,340
If we inject him with Mannitol
within a short period again,

16
00:02:24,379 --> 00:02:26,099
he might experience kidney failure.

17
00:02:26,659 --> 00:02:28,259
If so, why didn't you wait for me?

18
00:02:28,459 --> 00:02:30,340
Who will bear the responsibility
if something happens to the patient?

19
00:02:40,259 --> 00:02:41,300
(Door's open.)

20
00:02:42,860 --> 00:02:43,539
(2012 Jiangzhou, China)
I can't stand it anymore.

21
00:02:43,539 --> 00:02:44,179
Be careful.

22
00:02:44,459 --> 00:02:45,700
I'm sure my heel is bleeding.

23
00:02:50,099 --> 00:02:50,940
Let me take a look.

24
00:02:51,539 --> 00:02:52,500
It's fine.

25
00:02:56,739 --> 00:02:57,819
Let me clean it for you.

26
00:02:58,019 --> 00:02:58,940
It's fine. I can do it myself.

27
00:02:59,179 --> 00:03:00,379
What are you saying? I have to do it.

28
00:03:24,539 --> 00:03:25,340
Give me your foot.

29
00:03:28,259 --> 00:03:29,140
Bear with it.

30
00:03:31,060 --> 00:03:33,099
The person who designed high heels

31
00:03:33,140 --> 00:03:34,500
must be out to torture people.

32
00:03:35,580 --> 00:03:36,659
Your heel is already bleeding.

33
00:03:37,179 --> 00:03:37,899
Precisely.

34
00:03:38,780 --> 00:03:40,940
This is my last time wearing high heels.

35
00:03:41,099 --> 00:03:41,940
I won't wear it again.

36
00:03:44,819 --> 00:03:46,300
You only did it for the wedding, right?

37
00:03:46,780 --> 00:03:47,619
The wedding was tiring.

38
00:03:47,659 --> 00:03:48,500
I smiled the entire day.

39
00:03:48,500 --> 00:03:49,259
My face is numb now.

40
00:03:49,259 --> 00:03:50,300
I don't think I can smile now.

41
00:03:53,700 --> 00:03:55,140
You're smiling right now.

42
00:03:55,739 --> 00:03:57,140
I will never hold a wedding again.

43
00:03:59,420 --> 00:04:00,619
Again?

44
00:04:01,659 --> 00:04:02,819
Don't tell me you want to
hold another wedding?

45
00:04:03,340 --> 00:04:04,259
With whom?

46
00:04:08,780 --> 00:04:09,500
Give me the other foot.

47
00:04:20,900 --> 00:04:21,620
It doesn't hurt anymore.

48
00:04:23,339 --> 00:04:24,020
Done.

49
00:04:25,219 --> 00:04:26,180
I'll get you your slippers.

50
00:04:36,819 --> 00:04:37,939
Leave it over there. I'll clean it up.

51
00:04:38,539 --> 00:04:39,219
Here.

52
00:04:40,819 --> 00:04:41,700
Go and take a bath.

53
00:04:41,700 --> 00:04:43,059
I'll change the band-aid for you
once you're done.

54
00:04:46,580 --> 00:04:47,939
Untie this for me.

55
00:06:16,900 --> 00:06:17,700
Hello?

56
00:06:17,860 --> 00:06:18,620
(Hello, Dr. Ning.)

57
00:06:18,939 --> 00:06:19,580
(Are you busy?)

58
00:06:19,659 --> 00:06:20,740
(We have an emergency over here.)

59
00:06:20,740 --> 00:06:21,499
(We require your assistance.)

60
00:06:22,860 --> 00:06:23,580
What's going on?

61
00:06:23,580 --> 00:06:25,219
(The patient has
intracranial hemorrhage.)

62
00:06:25,379 --> 00:06:26,339
(It's pretty severe.)

63
00:06:26,620 --> 00:06:27,539
What about the other doctors?

64
00:06:27,539 --> 00:06:28,460
(Those on duty are already here.)

65
00:06:28,700 --> 00:06:29,580
(But we lack manpower.)

66
00:06:29,620 --> 00:06:30,219
You guys lack manpower?

67
00:06:30,219 --> 00:06:30,499
(That's right.)

68
00:06:32,499 --> 00:06:34,259
Do you guys know what day it is today?

69
00:06:34,460 --> 00:06:35,059
(Dr. Ning,)

70
00:06:35,259 --> 00:06:36,460
(I know today's your wedding day.)

71
00:06:36,700 --> 00:06:37,779
(But this is an emergency.)

72
00:06:38,020 --> 00:06:39,339
(Please come here immediately.)

73
00:06:39,819 --> 00:06:40,539
Fine.

74
00:06:40,939 --> 00:06:42,379
Alright, I understand.

75
00:06:43,099 --> 00:06:43,980
I'll head there immediately.

76
00:06:49,059 --> 00:06:49,819
Liuzheng,

77
00:06:50,819 --> 00:06:51,779
