78
00:06:51,819 --> 00:06:52,539
I have to go.

79
00:06:52,539 --> 00:06:53,980
Go to sleep after you're done bathing.
Don't wait for me.

80
00:06:54,300 --> 00:06:55,779
I'll be done in a second!

81
00:07:09,100 --> 00:07:11,940
(Beiya Hospital)

82
