84
00:07:47,700 --> 00:07:48,499
Periosteal elevator.

85
00:07:54,300 --> 00:07:55,900
I'm done. It's your turn to bathe.

86
00:08:06,300 --> 00:08:07,140
Where did he go?

87
00:08:09,499 --> 00:08:10,300
Where are you?

88
00:08:13,620 --> 00:08:15,259
