89
00:08:18,020 --> 00:08:19,180
Ready or not, here I come.

90
00:08:31,379 --> 00:08:32,579
I saw you!

91
00:08:39,820 --> 00:08:40,740
Ning?

92
00:08:41,899 --> 00:08:42,899
I don't feel like playing anymore.

93
00:08:42,940 --> 00:08:43,980
Show yourself.

94
00:08:44,180 --> 00:08:45,300
Where did he go?

95
