118
00:11:44,500 --> 00:11:45,899
When did you tell me that?

119
00:11:46,380 --> 00:11:47,620
When you were bathing.

120
00:11:48,899 --> 00:11:49,860
The ER needs me.

121
00:11:49,860 --> 00:11:50,659
I have to go.

122
00:11:50,659 --> 00:11:52,219
Go to sleep after you're done bathing.
Don't wait for me.

123
00:11:52,459 --> 00:11:53,820
I'll be done in a second!

124
00:11:59,180 --> 00:12:00,940
I thought you told me to hurry up.

125
00:12:02,339 --> 00:12:03,940
The hospital told me to hurry up.

126
00:12:06,260 --> 00:12:07,380
Did you sleep here the entire night?

127
00:12:08,500 --> 00:12:09,260
Isn't it cold?

128
