Come. Let's go inside.

130
00:12:13,740 --> 00:12:14,740
I'll cuddle you.

131
00:12:15,300 --> 00:12:15,899
You must be hungry.

132
00:12:15,940 --> 00:12:16,899
I'll cook something for you.

133
00:12:16,899 --> 00:12:17,740
It's okay.

134
00:12:17,899 --> 00:12:19,339
Sit down. I'll be done in a second.

135
00:12:19,940 --> 00:12:20,579
Just sit here.

136
00:12:37,139 --> 00:12:38,339
How many eggs would you like?

137
00:12:38,699 --> 00:12:39,820
One is enough.

138
