139
00:15:19,980 --> 00:15:20,459
Morning, Deputy Manager Ning.

140
00:15:20,579 --> 00:15:21,300
- Morning, Deputy Manager Ning.
- Morning.

141
00:15:23,099 --> 00:15:23,899
Morning, Deputy Manager Ning.

142
00:15:23,899 --> 00:15:24,620
Morning.

143
00:15:36,380 --> 00:15:38,420
(Beiya Hospital)

144
00:15:54,019 --> 00:15:55,180
Hello, mister.

145
00:15:55,180 --> 00:15:56,019
I was here first.

146
00:15:56,019 --> 00:15:56,940
I was trying to reverse my car

147
00:15:56,940 --> 00:15:57,659
and park into the spot.

148
00:15:57,699 --> 00:15:58,779
Didn't you see my car?

149
00:15:58,779 --> 00:16:00,099
Do you understand the meaning of
first come first served?

150
00:16:00,260 --> 00:16:01,339
Sorry about that. I didn't see you.

151
00:16:01,380 --> 00:16:01,940
Sorry about that.

152
00:16:02,620 --> 00:16:03,579
Hurry and shift your car.

153
00:16:19,860 --> 00:16:21,019
Hey, come back!

154
00:16:21,219 --> 00:16:22,620
You don't plan on shifting your car?

155
00:16:22,779 --> 00:16:24,539
I have an emergency.
Find another parking spot.

156
00:16:24,820 --> 00:16:26,620
Do you think you're the only one
with an emergency here?

157
00:16:28,060 --> 00:16:28,899
Come back!

158
00:16:28,899 --> 00:16:30,139
Are you even a man?

159
00:16:33,219 --> 00:16:35,099
What kind of person is this?

160
00:16:39,099 --> 00:16:39,820
Dr. Cheng!

161
00:16:40,940 --> 00:16:41,620
You're back?

162
00:16:42,659 --> 00:16:43,459
I'm back.

163
00:16:43,539 --> 00:16:44,860
Bai, Fan.

164
00:16:45,339 --> 00:16:46,740
How did your teaching

165
00:16:46,779 --> 00:16:47,500
at the subordinate unit go?

166
00:16:47,740 --> 00:16:49,620
My students were very passionate.

167
00:16:50,139 --> 00:16:52,019
Didn't you take the chance to make
one of your students your girlfriend?

168
00:16:52,820 --> 00:16:53,860
All of them were guys.

169
00:16:54,579 --> 00:16:55,940
I have to tell you something then.

170
00:16:55,940 --> 00:16:57,139
Two gorgeous ladies

171
00:16:57,180 --> 00:16:58,380
joined our department
while you were away.

172
00:16:58,940 --> 00:16:59,980
Really?

173
00:17:00,219 --> 00:17:02,260
The Department of Neurosurgery

174
00:17:02,260 --> 00:17:02,940
finally has girls now?

175
00:17:03,019 --> 00:17:04,380
One of them is gentle
while the other is feisty.

176
00:17:04,860 --> 00:17:06,020
Both of them are good-looking.

177
00:17:07,020 --> 00:17:08,620
Since I just came back,

178
00:17:08,740 --> 00:17:10,059
you guys should introduce me

179
00:17:10,099 --> 00:17:10,980
in a grand manner later.

180
00:17:11,140 --> 00:17:11,939
- Sure.
- Sure.

181
00:17:12,099 --> 00:17:12,660
Just leave it to me.

182
00:17:12,860 --> 00:17:13,780
I'll leave it to you guys.
Make it grand, okay?

183
00:17:13,780 --> 00:17:14,579
Let's go and get changed.

184
00:17:14,579 --> 00:17:15,500
Let's go.

185
00:17:25,299 --> 00:17:26,179
Dr. Ding,

186
00:17:26,219 --> 00:17:27,419
why are you late today?

187
00:17:27,660 --> 00:17:28,500
Don't bring it up.

188
00:17:28,500 --> 00:17:30,140
A despicable guy

189
00:17:30,140 --> 00:17:31,059
stole my parking spot just now.

190
00:17:31,059 --> 00:17:31,939
It was so infuriating.

191
00:17:32,500 --> 00:17:33,699
If I see him again,

192
00:17:33,699 --> 00:17:35,780
I'll crack his head open
with my high heels.

193
00:17:35,939 --> 00:17:36,699
Don't be angry.

194
00:17:36,699 --> 00:17:37,740
I'll crack his head open for you

195
00:17:37,780 --> 00:17:39,020
if you see him again.

196
00:17:39,419 --> 00:17:40,900
Nice. It's a promise then.

197
00:17:41,179 --> 00:17:41,860
By the way,

198
00:17:41,939 --> 00:17:43,260
let me introduce an expert to you.

199
00:17:43,419 --> 00:17:44,219
Dr. Cheng?

200
00:17:45,299 --> 00:17:46,500
This is our attending doctor,

201
00:17:46,500 --> 00:17:47,819
Dr. Cheng Zhouyu.

202
00:17:48,419 --> 00:17:50,260
He just came back from his
teaching duty

203
00:17:50,260 --> 00:17:50,980
at a subordinate unit.

204
00:17:51,699 --> 00:17:52,900
His skills are superb.

205
00:17:52,980 --> 00:17:54,780
He's only second to Dr. Ning.

206
00:17:55,699 --> 00:17:56,939
Second to Dr. Ning?

207
00:17:57,179 --> 00:17:58,980
They're evenly matched.

208
00:17:59,419 --> 00:18:00,020
That's right.

209
00:18:00,020 --> 00:18:01,419
He's one of the
main forces of our hospital.

210
00:18:02,140 --> 00:18:03,299
We meet again.

211
00:18:03,299 --> 00:18:04,099
Yeah.

212
00:18:05,419 --> 00:18:06,140
Do you two know each other?

213
00:18:06,419 --> 00:18:07,219
We do.

214
00:18:07,380 --> 00:18:08,419
Didn't you say

215
00:18:08,419 --> 00:18:09,540
you wanted to crack
his head open for me?

216
00:18:10,579 --> 00:18:12,059
Take this for me. Go ahead.

217
00:18:15,179 --> 00:18:17,219
There was a misunderstanding
at the car park just now.

218
00:18:17,860 --> 00:18:20,459
Is this the feisty one
or the gentle one?

219
00:18:20,459 --> 00:18:21,819
This is the feisty one.

220
00:18:21,819 --> 00:18:22,660
She's amazing, right?

221
00:18:22,740 --> 00:18:23,459
She's the feisty one?

222
00:18:23,860 --> 00:18:24,780
What about the gentle one?

223
00:18:24,780 --> 00:18:25,860
She went to do her rounds with Dr. Ning.

224
00:18:25,860 --> 00:18:26,660
She's doing her rounds?

225
00:18:28,459 --> 00:18:29,620
You guys should go on your rounds too.

226
00:18:29,620 --> 00:18:30,579
I'll wait for Ning to return.

227
00:18:31,939 --> 00:18:32,540
Let's go.

228
00:18:36,219 --> 00:18:37,860
The patient in Bed tenth
is recovering well.

229
00:18:38,620 --> 00:18:39,540
Observe his condition.

230
00:18:41,099 --> 00:18:42,459
The crucial period is three days
after the operation.

231
00:18:42,459 --> 00:18:43,620
Keep an eye on the patient's condition.

232
00:18:43,620 --> 00:18:44,299
Okay.

233
00:18:45,020 --> 00:18:45,699
Resume your work.

234
00:18:46,059 --> 00:18:46,660
Okay.

235
00:18:54,740 --> 00:18:55,620
What are you doing?

236
00:18:57,620 --> 00:18:58,540
Hello, Deputy Manager Ning.

237
00:18:58,540 --> 00:18:59,260
Hello.

238
00:19:02,020 --> 00:19:03,740
We have to keep our distance.

239
00:19:07,020 --> 00:19:07,740
But why?

240
00:19:09,900 --> 00:19:12,579
Ding Yiyuan is keeping
a close eye on me.

241
00:19:12,579 --> 00:19:14,339
Do you think I'll have it easy

242
00:19:14,339 --> 00:19:16,219
if she finds out about our relationship?

243
00:19:19,059 --> 00:19:20,140
What's there to be afraid of?

244
00:19:20,419 --> 00:19:22,140
Why can't we disclose
our divorce to other people?

245
00:19:23,020 --> 00:19:24,339
It might not matter to you.

246
00:19:24,620 --> 00:19:25,980
But have you considered my feelings?

247
00:19:26,860 --> 00:19:29,140
An ex-wife as the student
of her ex-husband?

248
00:19:29,620 --> 00:19:30,860
Even a terrible student can

249
00:19:30,860 --> 00:19:32,459
write a drama based on that.

250
00:19:32,500 --> 00:19:33,699
You're out of your mind.

251
00:19:34,360 --> 00:19:35,240
(Nurse Station)

252
00:19:47,900 --> 00:19:49,140
Why did you come back?

253
00:19:49,740 --> 00:19:50,900
I've already been away for two months.

254
00:19:50,900 --> 00:19:52,059
Of course I need to come back.

255
00:19:53,500 --> 00:19:55,459
I heard that you took in
a female student.

256
00:19:55,540 --> 00:19:56,540
And, she's quite beautiful.

257
00:19:57,620 --> 00:19:58,339
Who did you hear that from?

258
00:19:58,660 --> 00:19:59,579
That doesn't matter.

259
00:19:59,860 --> 00:20:00,579
How old is she?

260
00:20:00,699 --> 00:20:01,540
Is she taken?

261
00:20:01,819 --> 00:20:03,059
She's not suitable for you.

262
00:20:03,219 --> 00:20:05,819
How would you know when
we haven't met each other yet?

263
00:20:06,059 --> 00:20:08,059
What if she likes someone like me?

264
00:20:08,059 --> 00:20:09,059
Which part of you is likable?

265
00:20:09,059 --> 00:20:10,299
Your smelly feet?

266
00:20:10,339 --> 00:20:11,339
Wear your shoes.

267
00:20:11,780 --> 00:20:12,980
Compliment me

268
00:20:12,980 --> 00:20:14,339
when you introduce me to her later.

269
00:20:14,380 --> 00:20:15,980
Don't forget. You owe me a girlfriend.

270
00:20:16,219 --> 00:20:17,260
I owe you a girlfriend?

271
00:20:17,260 --> 00:20:17,860
When?

272
00:20:18,059 --> 00:20:19,339
Weren't you the one

273
00:20:19,459 --> 00:20:20,860
who introduced Ruan to me back then?

274
00:20:21,579 --> 00:20:22,740
Ruan?

275
00:20:22,819 --> 00:20:24,339
Do you think she'll fall for
a person like you?

276
00:20:24,579 --> 00:20:25,500
I don't care.

277
00:20:25,500 --> 00:20:27,579
I'm busy every day even though
I'm at this age.

278
00:20:27,579 --> 00:20:28,260
I just expect

279
00:20:28,260 --> 00:20:30,900
to get a girlfriend within our department now.

