584
00:39:57,540 --> 00:39:58,060
It's fine.

585
00:39:58,060 --> 00:39:59,219
Please wash your hands.

586
00:39:59,379 --> 00:40:00,540
Tell her to be

587
00:40:00,580 --> 00:40:01,419
